<div class="main-container">
  <div class="text-center">
    <h3>モノと人との出会い</h3>
    <h3>DanshaList</h3>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="text-center">
  <h5>使わなくなった大切なモノを<br>誰かに使ってもらいたくありませんか？</h5>
</div>
<div class="main">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <% @items.each do |item| %>
        <div class="col-md-4 text-center mt-5 mb-5">
          <%if item.image?%>
            <%= image_tag item.image.url, :size => '200x200' %>
          <% else %>
            <%= image_tag "/assets/default.jpeg", :size => '200x200' %>
          <% end %>
          <div>
            <%= link_to item.name, item %>
              
          </div>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
    <div class="pull-right mt-3">
      <%= paginate @items %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
